          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<strong>1970s and Beyond</strong>",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_wtDrDx": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Over the years, through countless trials and tribulations, Dave mastered the sales career. He eventually became the West Bend Company’s largest cookware distributor in the world. He hired thousands of college students to sell cookware to single girls for their hope chests and created a cooking demonstration that is still performed at over 3,000 events in America to this day.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
